msgid "Constants"
msgstr "常量"

#: ../../library/pyb.DAC.rst:131
msgid "NORMAL mode does a single transmission of the waveform in the data buffer,"
msgstr "NORMAL 模式对数据缓冲区中的波形进行单次传输，"

#: ../../library/pyb.DAC.rst:135
msgid ""
"CIRCULAR mode does a transmission of the waveform in the data buffer, and"
" wraps around to the start of the data buffer every time it reaches the "
"end of the table."
msgstr "CIRCULAR 模式对数据缓冲区中的波形进行传输，并在达到表格末尾时重新回到表格的开头。"
